channel.title: Can't Log in...Please help =)
channel.description:
OK, whenever I try to log in on ANY server, it says "Server down..." blah blah blah. On either No-ip OR Hamachi, it does that. Maybe I don't have the right Java? If that's true, could you tell me the name so I can download it?
Which brings me to my other point: Whenver I try to compile my Hamachi server, it says "Javac is not recognized as an internal or external command...". I think that also means I don't have the right Java. Please tell me the name of what you guys use as of June 16 2007 for creating servers, either Hamachi or No-ip. Thanks.
